    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The board of public works today\nsent a letter to Northern Pacific\nrailway officials in this city order\ning them to Immediately Make all\ncrossings in this city safe to pub\nlie travel and to board the grades\nbetween the tracks and put them in\nsome such shape that will be in\nkeeping with the conditions on the\nstreets which they cross.\n\n\nThis action was called forth by\nthe recent accident on Wall street,\nwhere a delivery horse was struck\nand killed by a flying switch en-\nCINE."
    }
